text: Maarit Raiskio (born 5 February 1964) is a Finnish equestrian. She competed in two events at the 1988 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1964 births Category:Living people Category:Finnish female equestrians Category:Olympic equestrians of Finland Category:Equestrians at the 1988 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Pori
